docs/reports/terminal/20260518-205333_sync-diagnose-rule-evidence-governance.log:193:docs/handoff/CURRENT_HANDOFF.md:282:- Completed: PR #332 merged terminal branch-safety handling. Logged runs should use `./ns terminal-clean-check` instead of plain `git status --short` emptiness checks. Normal FAIL handoff is now: run fails under `run-logged`, execute `./ns terminal-upload`, then answer `f`/`fail`.
