docs/reports/terminal/v0.3.36_standard_error_contract_prep.log:906:docs/reports/terminal/20260518-190206_standard-error-guard-inspection.log:43:54:Do not commit a repository log file while the current process is still writing to it. Long scripts must tee into a temporary log outside `docs/reports/terminal/`, then finalize the completed log into `docs/reports/terminal/*.log` with `./ns terminal-finalize <tmp-log> <name>` before staging, committing, and pushing. The finalized log must contain an explicit `### RESULT: PASS ###`, `### RESULT: FAIL ###`, or `### RESULT: PENDING ###` marker.
