AGENTS.md:349:When the marker is `PASS`, the human can reply with a short acknowledgement such as `d`. When the marker is `FAIL`, the relevant output should be shared for diagnosis.
AGENTS.md:351:Terminal blocks must avoid heredocs and risky multi-line `python -c` strings. Prefer small script files under `tmp/`, explicit virtualenv paths such as `.venv/bin/python`, and quote-safe one-line shell operations.
CHANGELOG.md:1:## v0.3.36 - Unreleased
CHANGELOG.md:8:- Released the pre-GUI core and CLI consolidation line with verified Zenodo version DOI `10.5281/zenodo.20316280`.
CHANGELOG.md:10:- Wired finalize-guard shell classification to the tested Python decision core.
CHANGELOG.md:12:- Extracted release-gate behavior into the tested Python `release_gate_core`, leaving `tools/ns_release_gate.sh` as a thin adapter.
CHANGELOG.md:16:- Hardened the pre-GUI portable Python core by adding typed work-order unit-test coverage, explicit `./ns dev-local-feature-gate` routing, and a shared local feature gate core.
CHANGELOG.md:17:- Added a tested finalize-guard decision core with module CLI/render contract and reachable superseded-branch handling.
CHANGELOG.md:52:- Tkinter implementation remains explicitly deferred until after this contract baseline is released and post-release verified.
CHANGELOG.md:62:- Hardened communication artifact GC before GUI readiness: symlink rejection, protected evidence coverage, TTL-based local tmp-log cleanup, and GC closeout documentation.
CHANGELOG.md:64:- Recorded quote-guard hardening for nested shell/Python quote-layer failures.
CHANGELOG.md:107:- Add no-copy release shortcut commands for release preparation, release gating, and confirmation-gated release publishing.
CHANGELOG.md:120:- Keep the GUI read-only by default: bounded and destructive actions remain blocked by the shared cockpit action layer.
CHANGELOG.md:131:- Added a numbered `./ns select` entry to `./ns-menu` without adding new shell execution logic.
CHANGELOG.md:151:- Used raw Typer output for JSON so consumers can parse it without Rich rendering artifacts.
CHANGELOG.md:159:- Added `./ns cockpit-run <action-id>` as a conservative repo-local shortcut to the existing cockpit action layer.
CHANGELOG.md:162:- Added regression coverage for shortcut routing, menu visibility, and shell-safety constraints.
CHANGELOG.md:181:- Added repo-local `./ns cockpit` and `./ns actions` shortcuts plus matching `./ns-menu` entries.
CHANGELOG.md:182:- Documented the future shared action-layer direction for CLI, shell/menu adapters, and a later Tkinter cockpit without shell-quoting based command synthesis.
CHANGELOG.md:183:- Refreshed README, documentation coverage, TEST_GATES, STATUS, and CURRENT_HANDOFF after the Local Cockpit Foundation merge.
CHANGELOG.md:198:- Added advisory-only `agentic-kit patterns list` and `agentic-kit patterns show <id>` commands.
CHANGELOG.md:203:- Added repo-local workflow-item shortcuts for listing, showing, running, uploading, and status checks through `./ns` aliases.
CHANGELOG.md:206:- Refreshed state and handoff documentation after the workflow-item shortcut and current-work isolation slices.
CHANGELOG.md:212:Release candidate for the workflow shortcut and Pattern Advisor contract line.
