docs/STATUS.md:283:- v0.3.34 pre-GUI portable-core hardening continued with a pure Python finalize-guard decision core in `src/agentic_project_kit/finalize_guard.py`. This models idempotent completion, noop branches, PR-needed branches, superseded branches, and relevant conflict failures before replacing the shell runner.
