docs/ideas/LAYERED_CLI_USABILITY.md:167:A later Tkinter cockpit should not become a separate command system. It should be a presentation and selection layer over the same explicit cockpit action registry used by `agentic-kit cockpit actions`, `agentic-kit cockpit actions --json`, and `agentic-kit cockpit run <action-id>`.
