docs/planning/GUI_COCKPIT_EXPANSION_ROADMAP.md:6:Review policy: review before implementation, after each GUI milestone, and before any write-capable GUI behavior is added.
docs/planning/GUI_COCKPIT_EXPANSION_ROADMAP.md:10:The local GUI cockpit should become the safe single-user control surface for agentic-project-kit. It must remain a presentation and orchestration layer over deterministic, testable project actions. It must not become a second command system.
