docs/reports/terminal/20260518-205333_sync-diagnose-rule-evidence-governance.log:129:docs/handoff/CURRENT_HANDOFF.md:19:PR #255 added an inspect-only cockpit action selection view. `agentic-kit cockpit select` renders a numbered action list from the central cockpit action registry without executing actions. `./ns select` delegates to that command, and `./ns-menu` exposes it as a numbered entry without adding new shell execution logic.
